@page "/"
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager

<PageTitle>Welcome</PageTitle>

<h3>Welcome to TaskFlow</h3>

<p>TaskFlow is a task management application that helps you stay organized and productive.</p>

<img src="~/images/taskflow.jpg" alt="TaskFlow" style="max-width: 400px; margin-top: 20px;">

<p>With TaskFlow, you can:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Create tasks with a title, description, due date, and priority.</li>
    <li>View, edit, and delete tasks.</li>
    <li>Assign tasks to specific users.</li>
    <li>Search and filter tasks based on various criteria.</li>
</ul>

<p>TaskFlow provides a user-friendly interface for managing tasks efficiently, helping you stay on top of your work and meet your deadlines.</p>

<p>
    <a href="@NavigationManager.ToAbsoluteUri("/tasks")">Get Started</a>
</p>
